{"type":null,"faqId":13442,"title":"G730-L075 手机自动关机或重启，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机自动关机或重启，若是可拆卸电池，可能是由于电池接触不良造成。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请取下电池后，使用棉布蘸取酒精擦拭电池和手机上的触点，重装电池后开机。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，长按电源键打开选项菜单，选择<b>重新启动</b>。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法打开选项菜单，请长按电源键</span><span> 10 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">秒以上，强制关机后开机或强制重启。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法打开选项菜单，请重装电池后开机。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若重启后仍然出现问题，可能是由于某些第三方应用程序不兼容。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">建议您备份重要数据后将手机恢复出厂设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若无法操作手机，请将手机强制升级。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入</span> <span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包，参考软件升级包中的升级指导操作。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":7,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4571","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1404702353000,"seriesProductName":"G730-L075","visitedTimes":946,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G730-L075","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}